import React from 'react'
import {Sidebar, Menu, Icon} from 'semantic-ui-react'

export default function MenuSidebar(props) {

    
    console.log(props.visible)
    return (
        <Sidebar
        as={Menu}
        color='blue'
        animation='overlay'
        icon='labeled'
        inverted
        vertical
        visible={props.visible}
        width='thin'
        direction='bottom'
      >
        <Menu.Item as='a'>
          <Icon name='home' />
          Home
        </Menu.Item>
        <Menu.Item as='a'>
          <Icon name='heart'/>
          About Me
        </Menu.Item>
        <Menu.Item as='a'>
          <Icon name='folder'/>
          Projects
        </Menu.Item>
        <Menu.Item as='a'>
          <Icon name='folder'/>
          Contact Me
        </Menu.Item>
      </Sidebar>)
}
